# ScienceBench Task 40

## Overview

- Domain: Bioinformatics
- Subtask Categories: Feature Engineering, Machine Learning
- Source: anikaliu/CAMDA-DILI
- Expected Output: MD_MCNC_RF.csv
- Output Type: Tabular

## Task

Train a random forest model to predict whether a given chemical structure has Drug-Induced Liver Injury (DILI) concerns, based on the given features. Add a ’label’ column and put the predicted labels (’DILI’ or ’NoDILI’) in the column.
